				<td colspan="2"><span>First off, in this context, I am defining a &quot;Twist&quot; as having active songs &quot;Icon in the song box&quot; or on a mob.
<br />

<br />
It is impossible to keep 5 songs active with (5 song icons up at ALL times) with no clickies.
<br />

<br />
It is tough to keep 4 songs active 100% of the time.  Missed notes, server vs pc timing, stuns and such can throw off your timing and make you drop to three or two even till you get your rythm back.
<br />

<br />
4 songs is the norm for me, if I have to mezz, HoS or slow, I drop one or more of the twist till I do whatever it is I need to do.
