				<td colspan="2"><span>I have a 4 song twist, but like folks have said, missed notes, lag, typing to group that takes longer than 3 seconds all change that to 3 songs quickly. On raids I drop it down to 2-3 essential songs since my computer isn't top of the line, and I don't want to risk missed notes. Or I twist the essential song, Song x, essential song, Song y, essential song, Song x, etc. Just to be sure that the one song I REALLY need to be singing is there. 
<br />

<br />
I can maintain 5 songs with an insta clicky item too, but I rarely do that anymore. Given the math on how long it takes to sing a song, I find it hard to believe you consistantly maintain 5 normal songs at all times. If you do.. go you! But, like others said, it's not about how much spam you make in your song window, it's about which spam you make! It's just plain silly to twist a song that you don't need just to impress the natives.<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
